title: 10,000 Keys to $1 Million
itunes:title: 10,000 Keys to $1 Million
description:
Episode 253 - If I gave you a 10,000 keys and said one key opens a door to $1 million would you try ever key to unlock that door? Yes, we all would! In this episode I talk about success, and how success leaves clues if you are willing to look for them.
